OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FWords by Bea Tridimas
OL,7,FCubans celebrated as a Russian tanker
OL,8,Fcarrying 730,000 barrels of oil docked
OL,9,Fon Tuesday, after a months-long energy
OL,10,Fblockade that has caused electricity
OL,11,Fblackouts, delays in healthcare and
OL,12,Fescalated an on-going economic crisis.
OL,14,FThe delivery is the first oil to reach
OL,15,Fthe island in three months after US
OL,16,FPresident Donald Trump cut access to
OL,17,Fthe island's main oil supplier `
OL,18,FVenezuela ` and threatened other
OL,19,Fsuppliers with tariffs, causing Mexico
OL,20,Fto also halt shipments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
