OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FSince returning to office, Trump has
OL,6,Fsignificantly tightened his economic
OL,7,Fsanctions against Cuba, telling CNN
OL,8,Flast month that it's only a "question
OL,9,Fof time" before the island could see a
OL,10,Fregime change.
OL,12,FHe has also hinted on numerous
OL,13,Foccasions that it is "next" on the
OL,14,Fadministration's agenda after the
OL,15,Fongoing war with Iran.
OL,17,F"He's doing some job, and your next
OL,18,Fone is going to be, we want to do that
OL,19,Fspecial Cuba," Trump said Thursday
OL,20,Freferring to his Secretary of State.
