OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,F"He's waiting. But he says, 'Let's get
OL,6,Fthis one finished first.' We could do
OL,7,Fthem all at the same time, but bad
OL,8,Fthings happen. If you watch countries
OL,9,Fover the years, you do them all too
OL,10,Ffast, bad things happen. We're not
OL,11,Fgoing to let anything bad happen to
OL,12,Fthis country."
OL,14,FBut what is happening in Cuba - and
OL,15,Fwhat could a US regime change mean for
OL,16,Fthe country?
OL,18,FHow did the latest conflict start?
