OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FIn January, Trump issued an executive
OL,6,Forder addressing what he called an
OL,7,F"extraordinary threat" posed by Cuban
OL,8,Fgovernment policies, actions and
OL,9,Fpractices.
OL,11,FThe order imposed tariffs on Cuba,
OL,12,Fwith Trump claiming it aligns itself
OL,13,Fwith countries and groups which the US
OL,14,Fconsiders hostile, including Russia,
OL,15,FChina, Iran, Hamas and Hezbollah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
