OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FWithout providing evidence, Trump also
OL,6,Faccused Cuba of inviting "hostile
OL,7,Fnations" to "base sophisticated
OL,8,Fmilitary and intelligence
OL,9,Fcapabilities" which he said is a
OL,10,Fthreat to national security.
OL,12,FThe order immediately prompted Mexico
OL,13,Fto pause oil shipments to Cuba,
OL,14,Falthough it said it was a "sovereign
OL,15,Fdecision" not made under pressure from
OL,16,Fthe US.
OL,18,FCuba is also an important issue to US
OL,19,FSecretary of State Marco Rubio, who is
OL,20,Fin charge of negotiations with the
OL,21,Fcountry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
