OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FRubio himself is Cuban-American and
OL,6,Fhas previously said the US wants "new
OL,7,Fpeople in charge" to fix the island's
OL,8,Flong-suffering economy.
OL,10,F"The people in charge, they don't know
OL,11,Fhow to fix (Cuba's economy)," Rubio
OL,12,Fsaid last week. "So they have to get
OL,13,Fnew people in charge. That's what has
OL,14,Fto happen."
