OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FThe fuel shortage has left the country
OL,6,Fin turmoil, hitting every sector from
OL,7,Ffood and healthcare to tourism and
OL,8,Feducation, exacerbating an already
OL,9,Fdeep economic crisis.
OL,11,FCuba heavily relies on oil for
OL,12,Felectricity generation, but only
OL,13,Fproduces around 40% of its own oil,
OL,14,Faccording to the International Energy
OL,15,FAgency.
OL,17,FThe island's crumbling electricity
OL,18,Fgrid has caused the country to
OL,19,Fexperience blackouts in recent years,
OL,20,Fwhich have become longer and more
OL,21,Ffrequent with the current blockade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
