OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FIn March, the country experienced
OL,6,Fthree nationwide blackouts, plunging
OL,7,Fmillions into darkness for several
OL,8,Fdays while power was restored.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, rubbish is piling up on
OL,11,Froads as fuel rations have hit rubbish
OL,12,Ftrucks and stopped farmers from
OL,13,Ftransporting food to markets.
OL,15,FHospitals are struggling to operate
OL,16,Fand the government has also cut school
OL,17,Fhours and postponed national sporting
OL,18,Fand cultural events.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
