OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FThe United Nations warned as early as
OL,6,FFebruary that the country faces
OL,7,F"humanitarian collapse" if the oil
OL,8,Fblockade continues and launched a $94
OL,9,Fmillion (#70.5 million) plan to
OL,10,Fsupport Cubans.
OL,12,FInternational airlines, including Air
OL,13,FCanada, Air France, and the US's
OL,14,FAmerican Airlines, Delta and Jet Blue,
OL,15,Fhave suspended flights to the island
OL,16,Fciting fuel shortages and grinding
OL,17,FCuba's tourism industry to a halt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
