OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FAs the Russian tanker arrived on the
OL,6,Fisland this week, Trump said its
OL,7,Fpassage was allowed for humanitarian
OL,8,Freasons, saying people "have to
OL,9,Fsurvive".
OL,11,FThe White House later confirmed that
OL,12,Fthe tanker's arrival is not a signal
OL,13,Fof a policy change.
OL,15,FHow does this link to Venezuela and
OL,16,FIran?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
