OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FSince Trump's return to office in
OL,6,FJanuary last year, the president has
OL,7,Flaunched campaigns to implement regime
OL,8,Fchange in Venezuela and Iran and has
OL,9,Fsuggested Cuba is next.
OL,11,FThe regime change in Venezuela has
OL,12,Fallowed Trump to stop sending oil from
OL,13,Fentering Cuba, even though the island
OL,14,Fdepends heavily on it.
OL,16,F"I do believe I'll be having the honor
OL,17,Fof taking Cuba. It's a big honor, I
OL,18,Fmean, whether I free it, take it. I
OL,19,Fthink I can do anything I want with
OL,20,Fit," Trump said from the White House
OL,21,Fon March 21.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
