OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FBut the president has refused to
OL,6,Fconfirm whether the US will use the
OL,7,Fsame level of force as it did to
OL,8,Fcapture Venezuelan President Nicolas
OL,9,FMaduro in January.
OL,11,FWhat is the US's history in Cuba?
OL,13,FCuba has been under strict economic
OL,14,Fembargo from the US since former
OL,15,Fleader Fidel Castro led a band of
OL,16,Frevolutionaries to overthrow the
OL,17,Fgovernment in 1959.
