OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FFormer President Barak Obama took
OL,6,Fsteps towards improving relations with
OL,7,FCuba, loosening restrictions and
OL,8,Fbecoming the first US president to
OL,9,Fvisit the island in 90 years.
OL,11,FBut Trump swiftly undid some of
OL,12,FObama's changes when first coming to
OL,13,Foffice in 2017 and intensified
OL,14,Feconomic pressure on the island last
OL,15,Fyear, by reimposing strict travel
OL,16,Frestrictions on US tourism and
OL,17,Fdoubling down on trade limits between
OL,18,Fthe countries.
OL,20,FWho holds power in Cuba?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
