OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FSince the 1959 revolution, Cuba has
OL,6,Fhad three leaders - Fidel, his brother
OL,7,FRaul and now Diaz-Canel, who took over
OL,8,Fas president in 2018, after Raul
OL,9,Fstepped down, ending nearly six
OL,10,Fdecades of Castro family rule.
OL,12,FCuba has been under one-party rule
OL,13,Fsince the revolution, with the
OL,14,FCommunist Party heading much of the
OL,15,Fcountry's economy and running the
OL,16,Fmedia, state and military.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
