OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FDiaz-Canel confirmed that the former
OL,6,Fpresident Raul has been representing
OL,7,FCuba at ongoing talks with the US,
OL,8,Falongside other members of the Cuban
OL,9,FCommunist Party.
OL,11,FTrump has claimed that Cuba is
OL,12,Fdesperate to come to a deal given its
OL,13,Fcurrent state of crisis, but Diaz-
OL,14,FCanel has confirmed that negotiations
OL,15,Fwill focus on ending the fuel embargo,
OL,16,Fnot political change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
