OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,F"Neither the president nor the
OL,6,Fposition of any leader in Cuba is up
OL,7,Ffor negotiation with the United
OL,8,FStates," Cuba's top diplomat for US
OL,9,Faffairs, Carlos Fernandez De Cossio,
OL,10,Ftold reporters in Havana.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, sightings of Raul's
OL,13,Fgrandson alongside Diaz-Canel have
OL,14,Fsparked rumours of his role in the
OL,15,Ffuture of the country.
