OL,3,CWhat is happening in Cuba?
OL,5,FRaul Guillermo Rodriguez Castro,
OL,6,Fnicknamed "El Cangrejo" (The Crab),
OL,7,Fattended Diaz-Canel's press
OL,8,Fconferences and took part in a meeting
OL,9,Fwith leaders of the Communist Party,
OL,10,Falthough has no known history within
OL,11,Fin the party.
OL,13,FWhat do Cubans think?
OL,15,FSince the crisis unfolded at the
OL,16,Fbeginning of the year, Cubans have
OL,17,Ftaken to the streets in rare protests,
OL,18,Fhitting pots and pans as a symbol of
OL,19,Fdiscontent.
